{"title":"榕树啊，我只想念你","authors":["陈秀喜"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":4,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"榕树啊，我只想念你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈秀喜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞过几重山与海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随云走过几百里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰看王宫，尖塔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸟瞰街道，田园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徘徊废墟，古迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眺望低山，树林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湄南河边也找不到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熟悉的你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焦急又寂然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喁喁哝哝安慰自己"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远离你反而"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心不断呼唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼到处寻觅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是故乡的象征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡的树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能到处都有？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"榕树啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的叶子是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我最初的乐器"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是我童年避雨的大伞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是晒谷场的凉亭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是老人茶，讲故事的好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是小土地公庙的保镖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是我家的门神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在异乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椰子树的怀抱里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是只想念你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔自东南亚之旅回来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九七七年十一月五日〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}